title: Priyanka Chopra on being lauded for 'Quantico', working in the west and more
text: Since Priyanka Chopra made her debut on American television last week on ABC’s new show, 'Quantico' (and in India last night on Star World) — she plays Alex Parrish, a young FBI recruit implicated in a terror attack -- her Twitter account has been flooded with applause.
